    • Constructor Detail

      • ProcessorWorker

        protected ProcessorWorker(Process<?> process,
                          ProjectInfoFile projectInfoFile,
                          ProjectInfoPlugin pluginInfo,
                          PluginMetaDataCollection.PluginMetaData pluginMetaData,
                          java.util.ArrayList<DataFileMetaData> cachedFiles)
        An implementation of ProcessWorker that handles the major processing of a list of raster files after being downloaded and handled by the Download framework. Output is used by the Indices framework. Meant to be ran on its own thread.
        Parameters:
        process - - the parent Process object to this threaded worker.
        projectInfoFile - - information about the project gotten from the project's info xml.
        pluginInfo - - information about the plugin being used for the acquired data files.
        pluginMetaData - - information relevant to this ProcessWorker about the plugin being used gotten from the plugin's info xml.
        cachedFiles - - the list of files to process in this ProcessWorker.
